    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the point of any of this lately. like, we're just tiny specks on a rock that's eventually gonna be swallowed by the sun, and then the whole universe just goes cold and dark anyway. everything we do, every struggle, every single person we love... it's all just a glitch in entropy. it feels kind of pointless to even keep trying, doesn't it?",
